data.description: Welcome to 107 Woods Drive, a unique Mid-Century split-level home in Arlington. Lots of unique features and upgrades. Main level features living room, main bedroom, dining room and breakfast nook. Upper level features three bedrooms- one oversized and 2 regular bedrooms. Lower level features a den and enclosed sunroom with backyard access. Brick fireplace has gas and ceramic logs. Beautiful and Main bedroom has dual closets and a large bathroom with separate shower and tub, extra-long vanity and linen cabinet. Mature landscaping, fenced yard, storage building, irrigation system, extra storage space in the garage. Convenient location to Dallas or Fort Worth.
